{
  "framework": "高效财务分析框架",
  "methodology": "七看八问",
  "version": "draft-0",
  "rules": [
    {
      "rule_id": "look-01",
      "sequence": 1,
      "category": "look",
      "title": "一看盈收与利润质量",
      "status": "implemented",
      "parallel_lane": "core",
      "data_status": "all-fields-present",
      "tables": [
        "fin_income",
        "fin_indicator",
        "fin_cashflow"
      ],
      "derived_metrics": [
        "profit_dedt",
        "grossprofit_margin",
        "netprofit_margin",
        "profit_to_gr",
        "n_cashflow_act",
        "n_income_attr_p",
        "c_pay_acq_const_fiolta",
        "net_profit_cash_ratio",
        "fcf",
        "net_profit_cash_ratio_avg",
        "net_profit_cash_ratio_below_one_years",
        "fcf_positive_years",
        "grossprofit_margin_declining_3y"
      ],
      "missing_data": [],
      "script": "look-01-profit-quality/scripts/look_01_profit_quality.py",
      "test_status": "passed",
      "review_status": "reviewed",
      "notes": "时间窗口默认最近3年，支持人工覆盖。仅取report_type=1合并报表。年报规则为end_date=12-31。2026-04-21 B1 升级：补齐框架要求的净现比 net_profit_cash_ratio = n_cashflow_act / n_income_attr_p（只在 n_income_attr_p>0 的年份纳入平均）、自由现金流 fcf = n_cashflow_act - c_pay_acq_const_fiolta（强口径），以及毛利率连续≥3年下降监测 grossprofit_margin_declining_3y。扣分规则在 orchestrator: 净现比均值<0.5 critical、任何年<1 warning、FCF 全负 critical、毛利率连续下降 warning。调用时先检测公司类型，金融类公司提示不适用。"
    },
    {
      "rule_id": "look-02",
      "sequence": 2,
      "category": "look",
      "title": "二看费用成本结构",
      "status": "implemented",
      "parallel_lane": "core",
      "data_status": "all-fields-present-rd-rate-derived",
      "tables": [
        "fin_income",
        "fin_indicator"
      ],
      "derived_metrics": [
        "rdexp_to_gr",
        "sell_exp_yoy",
        "admin_exp_yoy",
        "fin_exp_yoy",
        "rd_exp_yoy"
      ],
      "missing_data": [],
      "script": "look-02-cost-structure/scripts/look_02_cost_structure.py",
      "test_status": "passed",
      "review_status": "reviewed",
      "notes": "分析管理费用率、研发费用率、销售费用率、财务费用率，以及费用增长与营收增长的匹配度。销售、管理、财务费用率使用 fin_indicator 现成字段；研发费用率使用 rd_exp/total_revenue 派生。重点警示销售费用增长但营收增长停滞。调用时先检测公司类型，金融类公司提示不适用。已拆分为独立 skill：look-02-cost-structure。"
    },
    {
      "rule_id": "look-03",
      "sequence": 3,
      "category": "look",
      "title": "三看增长率趋势",
      "status": "implemented",
      "parallel_lane": "core",
      "data_status": "cagr-direct-acquisition-proxy",
      "tables": [
        "fin_income",
        "fin_balance",
        "fin_cashflow"
      ],
      "derived_metrics": [
        "revenue_cagr",
        "n_income_attr_p_cagr",
        "goodwill_to_assets",
        "acquisition_cash_to_revenue",
        "growth_mode_signal"
      ],
      "missing_data": [],
      "script": "look-03-growth-trend/scripts/look_03_growth_trend.py",
      "test_status": "passed",
      "review_status": "reviewed",
      "notes": "计算营业收入 CAGR 与归母净利润 CAGR，并通过商誉增长与取得子公司现金支出两个代理信号区分更偏内生增长还是可能包含并购驱动。CAGR 仅在起点和终点均为正数时计算，否则返回 null 与原因说明。调用时先检测公司类型，金融类公司提示不适用。已拆分为独立 skill：look-03-growth-trend。"
    },
    {
      "rule_id": "look-04",
      "sequence": 4,
      "category": "look",
      "title": "四看业务构成与市场分布",
      "status": "implemented",
      "parallel_lane": "core",
      "data_status": "sw-peers-available-report-text-human-loop",
      "tables": [
        "stk_info",
        "idx_sw_classify",
        "idx_sw_member_all",
        "idx_sw_l3_peers"
      ],
      "derived_metrics": [
        "peer_candidate_count",
        "business_composition_evidence_count",
        "overseas_sales_evidence_count",
        "customer_concentration_evidence_count"
      ],
      "missing_data": [
        "annual_report_full_text",
        "segment_revenue_mix",
        "regional_sales_split",
        "single_customer_sales"
      ],
      "script": "look-04-business-market-distribution/scripts/look_04_business_market_distribution.py",
      "test_status": "passed",
      "review_status": "reviewed",
      "notes": "先用 stk_info 与 idx_sw_l3_peers 提供结构化画像和申万三级同行池，再在缺少年报附注结构化数据时切换为 human-in-loop 工作流：要求提供最近3年年报全文或全文地址，从文本中提取业务构成、海外销售和客户集中度证据，并对同行公司执行同类分析。金融类公司不适用。已拆分为独立 skill：look-04-business-market-distribution。基线验证：000001.SZ 返回 not-applicable；000002.SZ 在无 bundle 时返回 human-in-loop-required 且能命中申万 L3 同行池；1年 synthetic bundle 验证业务构成/海外销售/客户集中度 3 类证据抽取通过。"
    },
    {
      "rule_id": "look-05",
      "sequence": 5,
      "category": "look",
      "title": "五看资产负债健康度",
      "status": "implemented",
      "parallel_lane": "core",
      "data_status": "cashflow-debt-available-hidden-liability-human-loop",
      "tables": [
        "fin_cashflow",
        "fin_balance",
        "fin_indicator"
      ],
      "derived_metrics": [
        "ocf_covers_investing",
        "fcf",
        "c_pay_acq_const_fiolta",
        "ocf_minus_capex",
        "ocf_covers_capex",
        "ocf_covers_capex_years",
        "interestdebt",
        "current_ratio",
        "debt_to_assets",
        "leverage_trend"
      ],
      "missing_data": [
        "annual_report_notes_text"
      ],
      "script": "look-05-balance-sheet-health/scripts/look_05_balance_sheet_health.py",
      "test_status": "passed",
      "review_status": "reviewed",
      "notes": "分析经营现金流覆盖、有息负债、偿债能力、资产负债率、隐性负债。2026-04-21 B2 升级：新增 OCF 覆盖资本开支检测 ocf_minus_capex = n_cashflow_act - c_pay_acq_const_fiolta，summary 输出 ocf_covers_capex_years / ocf_covers_capex_samples，扣分规则 orchestrator: 0 年覆盖 critical、<半数 warning。隐性负债仍需要年报附注全文（human-in-loop）。金融类公司不适用。"
    },
    {
      "rule_id": "look-06",
      "sequence": 6,
      "category": "look",
      "title": "六看投入产出效率",
      "status": "implemented",
      "parallel_lane": "core",
      "data_status": "structured-fields-present-headcount-human-loop",
      "tables": [
        "fin_income",
        "fin_balance",
        "fin_cashflow",
        "fin_indicator",
        "idx_sw_l3_peers",
        "stk_factor_pro"
      ],
      "derived_metrics": [
        "wc_per_revenue",
        "fix_assets_per_revenue",
        "revenue_per_labor_cost",
        "profit_per_labor_cost",
        "wc_trend",
        "revenue_per_employee",
        "profit_per_employee",
        "avg_labor_cost_per_employee",
        "per_capita_status",
        "per_capita_years_covered"
      ],
      "missing_data": [
        "employee_count"
      ],
      "script": "look-06-input-output-efficiency/scripts/look_06_input_output_efficiency.py",
      "test_status": "passed",
      "review_status": "reviewed",
      "notes": "分析营运资金/收入、固定资产/收入、人均投入产出，含行业基准对标。2026-04-21 B3 升级：DuckDB 无员工总数字段，默认 revenue/c_paid_to_for_empl 只是单位人力成本产出，不能替代人均口径。脚本新增 --employee-count-bundle 参数（人工从年报员工情况章节抄录 JSON）；未提供时 summary.per_capita_status = human-in-loop-required，脚本整体 status=partial，并在 human_in_loop_requests 列出缺口年份。禁止用任何代理公式估算 employee_count。缺数据本身不扣分，仅通过 human-in-loop 推动补齐。金融类公司不适用。"
    },
